      <title>戴利：2024年美联储三次降息的合理预测</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-04-02/daly-three-fed-rate-cuts-reasonable-projection-for-2024</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在内华达州举行的一次活动中，旧金山联邦储备银行行长玛丽·戴利表示，美联储 3 次降息是 2024 年的“合理基线”预测。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-04-02/daly-three-fed-rate-cuts-reasonable-projection-for-2024</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 02 Apr 2024 18:22:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>高盛部门抢购肯尼迪刘易斯在私人信贷赌注中的股份</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-02/goldman-unit-snaps-up-kennedy-lewis-stake-in-private-credit-bet</link>
      <description><![CDATA[高盛集团旗下 Petershill 部门同意购买肯尼迪刘易斯投资管理公司的少数股权——这是华尔街最大的公司对私人资产市场持续增长的又一赌注。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-02/goldman-unit-snaps-up-kennedy-lewis-stake-in-private-credit-bet</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 02 Apr 2024 18:21:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美联储官员称三次降息是2024年的合理基准</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-02/fed-s-daly-says-three-rate-cuts-is-reasonable-baseline-for-2024</link>
      <description><![CDATA[今年对货币政策决定进行投票的两名美联储官员表示，他们仍然预计美联储将在 2024 年降息三次，不过他们并不急于开始降低借贷成本。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-02/fed-s-daly-says-three-rate-cuts-is-reasonable-baseline-for-2024</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 02 Apr 2024 17:55:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>债券市场降息幅度小于美联储，损失加深</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-02/markets-back-to-seeing-fewer-rate-cuts-than-the-federal-reserve</link>
      <description><![CDATA[上周有一段时间，市场和美联储对于货币宽松的步伐达成了共识。这种情况并没有持续多久，国债投资者正在付出代价。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-02/markets-back-to-seeing-fewer-rate-cuts-than-the-federal-reserve</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 02 Apr 2024 10:20:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧佩克和地缘政治风险推动油价上涨至 85 美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-01/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-april-2</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国原油期货自 10 月份以来首次突破 85 美元，这是在 OPEC+ 减产、强劲需求和地缘政治风险加剧推动下上涨的最新里程碑。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-01/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-april-2</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Apr 2024 23:26:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>市场担心降息将被推迟，股市下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-01/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于强劲的经济数据和大宗商品的上涨引发了人们对主要央行将在更长时间内维持较高利率的猜测，全球股市和债券下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-01/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Apr 2024 21:58:44 GMT</pubDate>
